not much happening lately... Bree bought the Bolivian diaries from Che Guevara. Really interesting. Fidel Castro wrote the introduction which is basically a tirade on the 'Yankees'. Quite amusing. Che really is an intellegent guy but it's hard to know what to believe. Getting my lip pierced tomorrow! Sam told me a horror story about when she got hers done at a party and was ridiculousy drunk at the time. Apparently she bled so much she passed out... Moral for the kids is home piercings are a bad idea! Loving the new From First To Last album Heroine. Really good and different. Perfect second album really. It's got Wes Borland on bass-the old Limp Bizkit guitarist which was a bit of a suprise.
Adios.
